HvUt fJlZte pf-34_">If hand-washing, rinse the garment(s) in cold water and gently squeeze out the excess water.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-itWPBs dKPonY pf-35_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-37_">Lay the garment flat to dry.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-itWPBs dKPonY pf-38_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-40_">Iron on warm setting, if you feel ironing is necessary.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-itWPBs dKPonY pf-41_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-43_">Store your garments, preferably folded rather than hung.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-b891" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-igXgud lhtyiH pf-44_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-cjrPHo eOcrMz"><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-45_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gXRojI kCnmwO pf-46_"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-kHxTfl loKJhm pf-47_"><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-48_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-50_"><b>A few things to keep in mind:</b></span></p><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:10px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-gHjyzD dQAIat pf-51_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-itWPBs dKPonY pf-52_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-54_">Do not use fabric softener or bleach.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-itWPBs dKPonY pf-55_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-57_">Do not tumble dry or dry clean.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-itWPBs dKPonY pf-58_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-60_">Try not to twist or wring the fabric.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><script>
